						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in the <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of the Bhōgēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1554 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1476, Ānanda, Nija-Āshāḍha śu. 11,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1554 A.D., July 11.</hi></p>						

						<p>It is damaged and mentions god Bhōgēśvara of Pāmiḍi on the bank of the Pennā. The details of the grant are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
